  "body": "<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/modloader-fabric-beige\" alt=\"fabric badge\"> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mrg-speedometer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/1uwneI1f\" alt=\"modrinth badge\"></a>\n\n# Speedometer\nA simple mod that adds a speedometer to your GUI (‼️requaried <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config\">cloth-config</a>‼️)\n\nMod show your moving speed, yaw and pitch on left top of screen. It looks at the distance traveled in a short period of time (you can manage it).\n\n<img width=\"460\" height=\"258\" alt=\"2026-03-27_11 20 54\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/4f1ab243-eb8c-4cf8-b4c4-27b251a90721\" alt=\"gif with speedometer\"/>\n\n<img width=\"460\" height=\"258\" alt=\"2026-03-27_11 20 54\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1d3e6b0d-0474-41a0-b8bf-6c2e347c4467\" alt=\"screenshot with speedometer\"/>\n<img width=\"460\" height=\"258\" alt=\"2026-03-27_11 21 26\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e2201c18-7af5-4605-85fb-47e1a08ce571\" alt=\"screenshot with speedometer config menu\"/>",
